---
title: Alerts
---


<div class="row">
  <div class="small-12 columns">
    <h1>Alerts</h1>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="row u-mb-5">
  <div class="small-12 columns">
    <h2>Flash Alerts</h2>
    <p>Flash alerts are intended to be persistent until a user manually dismisses the alert by clicking a close button or performing a particular action. </p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="small-12 columns u-mb-5">
  <h3>Simple Flash Alert</h3>
  <p class="u-mb-3">Simple flash alerts are intended to notify users of a change or action, and are dismissed by clicking close.</p>
  <div class="Alert Alert--success">
    <div class="Alert-content">
      <span class="Alert-icon Icon--check"></span>
      <p>You successfully added $10 to your account!</p>
      <a class="Alert-close Icon--close"></a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="row u-mb-7">
  <div class="small-12 columns">
    <pre>
      <code><%= display_code('
<div class="Alert Alert--success">
  <div class="Alert-content">
    <span class="Alert-icon Icon--check"></span>
    <p>...</p>
    <a class="Alert-close Icon--close"></a>
  </div>
</div>') %></code>
    </pre>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="small-12 columns u-mb-5">
  <h3>Action Flash Alert</h3>
  <p class="u-mb-3">Action flash alerts are dismissed by going to another location via button click.</p>
  <div class="Alert Alert--failure">
    <div class="Alert-content">
      <p>Your account is in a strange state. You need to do something.</p>
      <a href="#" class="Button Button--alert">Do Something</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="row u-mb-7">
  <div class="small-12 columns">
    <pre>
      <code><%= display_code('
<div class="Alert Alert--failure">
  <div class="Alert-content">
    <p>...</p>
    <a href="#" class="Button Button--alert">Button</a>
  </div>
</div>') %></code>
    </pre>
  </div>
</div>


<div class="row u-mb-5">
  <div class="small-12 columns">
    <h2>Permanent Alerts</h2> 
    <p>Permanent alerts are persistent until a user takes specific action. The alert will auto dismiss once a user has completed this action.</p>
    <p class="small">NOTE: Permanent alerts are fixed and located on the bottom of the screen. These alerts are persistent across page changes.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="small-12 columns u-mb-5">
  <h3>Simple Flash Alert (persistent)</h3>
  <div class="Alert Alert--failure">
    <div class="Alert-content">
      <span class="Alert-icon Icon--close"></span>
      <p>Your account is currently locked</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

